{"surahDetails":{"id":80,"arabicName":"عبس","banglaName":"সে ভ্রু কুঁচকালো","englishName":"He frowned","enTranslatedName":"'Abasa","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":133,"totalLetters":538,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/080.mp3","totalAyah":42},"surah":{"id":80,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","bangl_text":"তিনি ভ্রূকুঞ্চিত করলেন এবং মুখ ফিরিয়ে নিলেন।","english_text":"The Prophet frowned and turned away","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","bangl_text":"কারণ, তাঁর কাছে এক অন্ধ আগমন করল।","english_text":"Because there came to him the blind man, [interrupting]","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি জানেন, সে হয়তো পরিশুদ্ধ হত","english_text":"But what would make you perceive, [O Muhammad], that perhaps he might be purified","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"অথবা উপদেশ গ্রহণ করতো এবং উপদেশ তার উপকার হত।","english_text":"Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","bangl_text":"পরন্তু যে বেপরোয়া","english_text":"As for he who thinks himself without need","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","bangl_text":"আপনি তার চিন্তায় মশগুল।","english_text":"To him you give attention","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","bangl_text":"সে শুদ্ধ না হলে আপনার কোন দোষ নেই।","english_text":"And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","bangl_text":"যে আপনার কাছে দৌড়ে আসলো","english_text":"But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080008.mp3"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","bangl_text":"এমতাবস্থায় যে, সে ভয় করে","english_text":"While he fears [Allah]","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080009.mp3"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","bangl_text":"আপনি তাকে অবজ্ঞা করলেন।","english_text":"From him you are distracted","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080010.mp3"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","bangl_text":"কখনও এরূপ করবেন না, এটা উপদেশবানী।","english_text":"No! Indeed, these verses are a reminder","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080011.mp3"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"অতএব, যে ইচ্ছা করবে, সে একে গ্রহণ করবে।","english_text":"So whoever wills may remember it","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080012.mp3"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","bangl_text":"এটা লিখিত আছে সম্মানিত","english_text":"[It is recorded] in honored sheets","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080013.mp3"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","bangl_text":"উচ্চ পবিত্র পত্রসমূহে","english_text":"Exalted and purified","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080014.mp3"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","bangl_text":"লিপিকারের হস্তে","english_text":"[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080015.mp3"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","bangl_text":"যারা মহৎ, পূত চরিত্র।","english_text":"Noble and dutiful","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080016.mp3"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"মানুষ ধ্বংস হোক, সে কত অকৃতজ্ঞ","english_text":"Cursed is man; how disbelieving is he","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080017.mp3"},{"id":18,"arabic_text":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","bangl_text":"তিনি তাকে কি বস্তু থেকে সৃষ্টি করেছেন","english_text":"From what substance did He create him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080018.mp3"},{"id":19,"arabic_text":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"শুক্র থেকে তাকে সৃষ্টি করেছেন, অতঃপর তাকে সুপরিমিত করেছেন।","english_text":"From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080019.mp3"},{"id":20,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তার পথ সহজ করেছেন","english_text":"Then He eased the way for him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080020.mp3"},{"id":21,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তার মৃত্যু ঘটান ও কবরস্থ করেন তাকে।","english_text":"Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080021.mp3"},{"id":22,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"এরপর যখন ইচ্ছা করবেন তখন তাকে পুনরুজ্জীবিত করবেন।","english_text":"Then when He wills, He will resurrect him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080022.mp3"},{"id":23,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","bangl_text":"সে কখনও কৃতজ্ঞ হয়নি, তিনি তাকে যা আদেশ করেছেন, সে তা পূর্ণ করেনি।","english_text":"No! Man has not yet accomplished what He commanded him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080023.mp3"},{"id":24,"arabic_text":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","bangl_text":"মানুষ তার খাদ্যের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করুক","english_text":"Then let mankind look at his food","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080024.mp3"},{"id":25,"arabic_text":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","bangl_text":"আমি আশ্চর্য উপায়ে পানি বর্ষণ করেছি","english_text":"How We poured down water in torrents","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080025.mp3"},{"id":26,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","bangl_text":"এরপর আমি ভূমিকে বিদীর্ণ করেছি","english_text":"Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts]","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080026.mp3"},{"id":27,"arabic_text":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তাতে উৎপন্ন করেছি শস্য","english_text":"And caused to grow within it grain","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080027.mp3"},{"id":28,"arabic_text":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","bangl_text":"আঙ্গুর, শাক-সব্জি","english_text":"And grapes and herbage","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080028.mp3"},{"id":29,"arabic_text":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","bangl_text":"যয়তুন, খর্জূর","english_text":"And olive and palm trees","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080029.mp3"},{"id":30,"arabic_text":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","bangl_text":"ঘন উদ্যান","english_text":"And gardens of dense shrubbery","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080030.mp3"},{"id":31,"arabic_text":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","bangl_text":"ফল এবং ঘাস","english_text":"And fruit and grass","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080031.mp3"},{"id":32,"arabic_text":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","bangl_text":"তোমাদেরও তোমাদের চতুস্পদ জন্তুদের উপাকারার্থে।","english_text":"[As] enjoyment for you and your grazing livestock","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080032.mp3"},{"id":33,"arabic_text":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর যেদিন কর্ণবিদারক নাদ আসবে","english_text":"But when there comes the Deafening Blast","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080033.mp3"},{"id":34,"arabic_text":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","bangl_text":"সেদিন পলায়ন করবে মানুষ তার ভ্রাতার কাছ থেকে","english_text":"On the Day a man will flee from his brother","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080034.mp3"},{"id":35,"arabic_text":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","bangl_text":"তার মাতা, তার পিতা","english_text":"And his mother and his father","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080035.mp3"},{"id":36,"arabic_text":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","bangl_text":"তার পত্নী ও তার সন্তানদের কাছ থেকে।","english_text":"And his wife and his children","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080036.mp3"},{"id":37,"arabic_text":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","bangl_text":"সেদিন প্রত্যেকেরই নিজের এক চিন্তা থাকবে, যা তাকে ব্যতিব্যস্ত করে রাখবে।","english_text":"For every man, that Day, will be a matter adequate for him","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080037.mp3"},{"id":38,"arabic_text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","bangl_text":"অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে উজ্জ্বল","english_text":"[Some] faces, that Day, will be bright","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080038.mp3"},{"id":39,"arabic_text":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","bangl_text":"সহাস্য ও প্রফুল্ল।","english_text":"Laughing, rejoicing at good news","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080039.mp3"},{"id":40,"arabic_text":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","bangl_text":"এবং অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে ধুলি ধূসরিত।","english_text":"And [other] faces, that Day, will have upon them dust","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080040.mp3"},{"id":41,"arabic_text":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","bangl_text":"তাদেরকে কালিমা আচ্ছন্ন করে রাখবে।","english_text":"Blackness will cover them","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080041.mp3"},{"id":42,"arabic_text":"أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","bangl_text":"তারাই কাফের পাপিষ্ঠের দল।","english_text":"Those are the disbelievers, the wicked ones","page":585,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/080042.mp3"}]}}